{"word":"ἐλπίζω","slug":"ἐλπίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐλπίζω</el></b> [<el>ἔλπω</el> ‘have hope’ via <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐλπίς\">ἐλπίς</a></el>] ‘look for’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> hope <a href='B:470 12:21'>Mt 12:21</a>; <a href='B:500 5:45'>J 5:45</a>; <a href='B:510 26:7'>Ac 26:7</a>; <a href='B:520 8:24'>Ro 8:24</a>; <a href='B:520 15:12'>15:12</a>; <a href='B:530 13:7'>1 Cor 13:7</a>; <a href='B:530 15:19'>15:19</a>; <a href='B:650 11:1'>Hb 11:1</a>; <a href='B:670 3:5'>1 Pt 3:5</a>.</b> In some <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> the context appears to connote relatively strong prospect of ready fulfillment, hence<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> expect <a href='B:490 6:34'>Lk 6:34</a>; <a href='B:490 23:8'>23:8</a>; <a href='B:490 24:21'>24:21</a>; <a href='B:510 24:26'>Ac 24:26</a>; <a href='B:520 15:24'>Ro 15:24</a>; <a href='B:530 16:7'>1 Cor 16:7</a>; <a href='B:540 8:5'>2 Cor 8:5</a>; <a href='B:570 2:19'>Phil 2:19</a>, <a href='B:570 2:23'>23</a>; <a href='B:610 3:14'>1 Ti 3:14</a>; <a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 22</a>; <a href='B:670 1:13'>1 Pt 1:13</a>; <a href='B:700 1:1'>2 J 12</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 14</a>.</b> (<el>ἐ.</el> is not used to express mere wishful thinking.) <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἑλόμενος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐλπίς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}